<para> <image type="html" name="Convex_decomposition_3-teaser.png"></image>
   Peter Hachenberger This packages provides a function for decomposing a bounded polyhedron into convex sub-polyhedra. The decomposition yields <formula id="1">$ O(r^2)$</formula> convex pieces, where <formula id="2">$ r$</formula> is the number of edges, whose adjacent facets form an angle of more than 180 degrees with respect to the polyhedron&apos;s interior. This bound is worst-case optimal.  <linebreak/>
